# LPC2148 DAC Sawtooth Wave Generator

This project demonstrates generating a **sawtooth waveform** using the DAC of the **LPC2148 ARM7 microcontroller**.

##  Hardware Connections
- **DAC0 Output Pin** → P0.25
- Connect this pin to an oscilloscope or DAC buffer circuit to observe the waveform.

## Code Highlights
- Configures **P0.25** as DAC output.
- Increments DAC value from 0 to 1023 (10-bit resolution).
- Generates a continuous **sawtooth wave**.

##  Usage
1. Load code into LPC2148 using Keil/Flash Magic.
2. Connect an oscilloscope probe to **P0.25**.
3. Observe the sawtooth waveform (0V – 3.3V).
